{"id": "1511032616592212049", "channel_id": "1511029815132557452", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "Q.恒常ガチャはどれを引けばいいの？", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T15:44:09.424000+00:00", "thread_id": "1511029815132557452"}
{"id": "1511033035200528445", "channel_id": "1511029815132557452", "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "content": "A.画像の通りです。\n超次元ガチャの引きが偏ってジェンキンが全く出ない！という場合は、ある程度のところで諦めて狂魔を回すのがオススメです。\nジェンキンは他限定アタッカーと入れ替えが可能です。", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T15:45:49.228000+00:00", "thread_id": "1511029815132557452", "attachments": [{"id": "1511033034953199878", "filename": "Screenshot_20260512-2313402.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 110015, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1511029815132557452/1511033034953199878/Screenshot_20260512-2313402.png?ex=6a3369ed&is=6a32186d&hm=4fd92aa2feac3074718a43369dd469b582cb24b26e63803fbcceefb28084167a&"}]}
